edits.expression:
CASE 
    WHEN `TITLE_HYPEN` = 2
          THEN SPLIT_PART(`TITLE`,'-',2)
    WHEN `TITLE_HYPEN` = 3
          THEN SPLIT_PART(`TITLE`,'-',3)
    WHEN `TITLE_HYPEN` = 4
          THEN SPLIT_PART(`TITLE`,'-',4)
    WHEN `TITLE_HYPEN` = 5
          THEN SPLIT_PART(`TITLE`,'-',5)
    WHEN `TITLE_HYPEN` IS NULL 
          THEN 'ERROR'
    ELSE 'UNACCOUNTED EDGE CASE'
END

CASE 
    WHEN `TITLE_HYPEN` = 2 
          THEN SPLIT_PART(`TITLE`,'-',1)
    WHEN `TITLE_HYPEN` = 3 
          THEN CONCAT(`TITLE Split 1`,', ',
                      `TITLE Split 2`)
    WHEN `TITLE_HYPEN` = 4 
          THEN CONCAT(`TITLE Split 1`,', ', 
                      `TITLE Split 2`,', ', 
                      `TITLE Split 3`)
    WHEN `TITLE_HYPEN` = 5 
          THEN CONCAT(`TITLE Split 1`,', ', 
                      `TITLE Split 2`,', ',
                      `TITLE Split 3`,', ',
                      `TITLE Split 4`)
    WHEN `TITLE_HYPEN` = 6
          THEN CONCAT(`TITLE Split 1`,', ', 
                      `TITLE Split 2`,', ',
                      `TITLE Split 3`,', ',
                      `TITLE Split 4`, ', ',
                      `TITLE Split 5`)
    ELSE "MAKE NEW EDGE CASE"
END

CASE 
    WHEN `LOCATION_COMMAS` = 1
          THEN SPLIT_PART(`LOCATION`, ',', 1)
ELSE ""
END

CASE 
  WHEN `LOCATION_COMMAS` = 1 
        THEN trim(SPLIT_PART(`LOCATION`,',',2))
  ELSE trim(`LOCATION`)
END
